1
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:24,640
<font color="#ffffff">A lowlife like you…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

2
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:27,240
<font color="#ffffff">shouldn't bring Dao down to his level.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

3
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:30,520
<font color="#ffffff">This guy is going to be our new artist.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

4
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:34,960
<font color="#ffffff">Track this guy down immediately.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

5
00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:37,360
<font color="#ffffff">I want him to release a single</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">under our label.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

6
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:41,080
<font color="#ffffff">I don't know what's wrong</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">with your channel. I can't watch anything.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

7
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:42,880
<font color="#ffffff">I think I know why.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

8
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:44,920
<font color="#ffffff">Our channel probably got hacked.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

9
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:47,720
<font color="#ffffff">Mr. Sompob will never find</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">Petch's channel again.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

10
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,480
<font color="#ffffff">Send some guys to beat him to a pulp.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

11
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,920
<font color="#ffffff">Hey!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

12
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:53,720
<font color="#ffffff">-Ouch!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Dao!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

13
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,440
<font color="#ffffff">What the hell are you doing? Put me down!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

14
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:58,600
<font color="#ffffff">-Put me down!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-Keep moving, and I'll do worse.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

15
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:01,600
<font color="#ffffff">PREVIOUSLY</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

16
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,480
<font color="#ffffff">Enough.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

17
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:41,920
<font color="#ffffff">Stop carrying me. I can walk.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

18
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,040
<font color="#ffffff">I won't.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

19
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:44,640
<font color="#ffffff">My shoulder hurts.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

20
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:46,920
<font color="#ffffff">Are you calling me fat?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

21
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:49,520
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, no!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

22
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:54,960
<font color="#ffffff">Sorry.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

23
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,560
<font color="#ffffff">I didn't mean to.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

24
00:04:57,880 --> 00:05:00,240
<font color="#ffffff">I just wanted to return your car keys.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

25
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,200
<font color="#ffffff">Hold on!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

26
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:10,000
<font color="#ffffff">You still haven't told me</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">who you fought with.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

27
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:12,040
<font color="#ffffff">Why were those thugs after you?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

28
00:05:13,280 --> 00:05:14,280
<font color="#ffffff">No idea.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

29
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:16,240
<font color="#ffffff">I've never seen them before.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

30
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:19,440
<font color="#ffffff">Then why did they attack you?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

31
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:20,520
<font color="#ffffff">Forget it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

32
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:24,760
<font color="#ffffff">Maybe I have a common face,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">and they got the wrong guy.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

33
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,720
<font color="#ffffff">Are you sure?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

34
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,080
<font color="#ffffff">I haven't crossed anyone,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

35
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:31,120
<font color="#ffffff">and I don't have any enemies.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

36
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:34,280
<font color="#ffffff">Should we go to the police?</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I can be your witness.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

37
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,200
<font color="#ffffff">No need.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

38
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,120
<font color="#ffffff">What's wrong now?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

39
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:40,200
<font color="#ffffff">I just don't want to waste your time.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

40
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:42,440
<font color="#ffffff">Are you saying I'm being nosy?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

41
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:43,880
<font color="#ffffff">No.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

42
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:46,920
<font color="#ffffff">But if we keep hanging out like this,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

43
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:49,360
<font color="#ffffff">your fiancé won't like it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

44
00:05:49,440 --> 00:05:51,440
<font color="#ffffff">Everything I do is wrong, isn't it?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

45
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:56,680
<font color="#ffffff">Just tell me what to do to make you happy.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

46
00:05:57,800 --> 00:06:00,040
<font color="#ffffff">We both know the answer.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

47
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,600
<font color="#ffffff">Let's just stay apart.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

48
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:04,880
<font color="#ffffff">Right.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

49
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:08,240
<font color="#ffffff">Act like strangers, you mean?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

50
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:10,120
<font color="#ffffff">Whatever makes you happy.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

51
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:11,080
<font color="#ffffff">Petch,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

52
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,800
<font color="#ffffff">you can treat me like an outsider.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

53
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,400
<font color="#ffffff">But for Mr. Nop,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

54
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:20,160
<font color="#ffffff">don't run away from him as you did to me.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

55
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:24,400
<font color="#ffffff">Do you have any idea how much that hurts?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

56
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,200
<font color="#ffffff">What?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

57
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,360
<font color="#ffffff">Petch beat up your guys?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

58
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,840
<font color="#ffffff">I was too careless,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

59
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:43,200
<font color="#ffffff">sending amateurs.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

60
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:44,760
<font color="#ffffff">Useless!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

61
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:46,480
<font color="#ffffff">Just go!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

62
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,640
<font color="#ffffff">Get out of my face!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

63
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:51,600
<font color="#ffffff">I will, but before I go,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I have something to tell you.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

64
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,880
<font color="#ffffff">What is it?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

65
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:57,400
<font color="#ffffff">When my guy got beaten up,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">he saw Petch with Dao.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

66
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,560
<font color="#ffffff">That bastard!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

67
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:00,280
<font color="#ffffff">Where is he?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

68
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:04,040
<font color="#ffffff">Well, he just brought Dao back</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">a moment ago.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

69
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:05,560
<font color="#ffffff">Petch!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

70
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,280
<font color="#ffffff">He's asking for it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

71
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:09,680
<font color="#ffffff">Let's give it to him!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

72
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,960
<font color="#ffffff">Dao!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

73
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,520
<font color="#ffffff">There you are.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

74
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:22,280
<font color="#ffffff">I was just about to invite you</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to watch us practice.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

75
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,920
<font color="#ffffff">Sure.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

76
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,440
<font color="#ffffff">Stop, Ake! Don't hurt him!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

77
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:26,800
<font color="#ffffff">Move!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

78
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,000
<font color="#ffffff">What's going on?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

79
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:30,520
<font color="#ffffff">-Hit him!</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">-You're only tough in a pack!<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

80
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,880
<font color="#ffffff">Hit him again, boss!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

81
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:35,080
<font color="#ffffff">Keep it coming, boss!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

82
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,640
<font color="#ffffff">Don't touch him!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

83
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,560
<font color="#ffffff">Ake, stop!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

84
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,920
<font color="#ffffff">What's going on here?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

85
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,400
<font color="#ffffff">Why are you being so brutal?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

86
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:46,840
<font color="#ffffff">This employee doesn't know his place.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

87
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:49,160
<font color="#ffffff">He needs to be taught a lesson.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

88
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:51,240
<font color="#ffffff">What do you mean?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

89
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:52,280
<font color="#ffffff">What did I do?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

90
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,720
<font color="#ffffff">You won't shut it?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

91
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:56,000
<font color="#ffffff">Natedao is my fiancée.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

92
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:58,000
<font color="#ffffff">You have no right to take her anywhere!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

93
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:00,000
<font color="#ffffff">What?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

94
00:08:00,840 --> 00:08:03,480
<font color="#ffffff">How did you know he brought me here?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

95
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:07,880
<font color="#ffffff">Or were those thugs your men?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

96
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:11,920
<font color="#ffffff">What thugs? I have no idea.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

97
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:16,200
<font color="#ffffff">I saw you and Petch on the CCTV.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

98
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:23,080
<font color="#ffffff">If you beat him up based just on that,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">that's terrible.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

99
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:26,120
<font color="#ffffff">Should I just stand by and watch?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

100
00:08:26,200 --> 00:08:27,560
<font color="#ffffff">You're my fiancée.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

101
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:29,480
<font color="#ffffff">I'm your fiancée, not your slave.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

102
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:31,640
<font color="#ffffff">Then how should I take this?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

103
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:36,480
<font color="#ffffff">We met by chance,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">and some thugs attacked us.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

104
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:39,720
<font color="#ffffff">I fell, and he just offered</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">to bring me back.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

105
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:42,799
<font color="#ffffff">If you don't believe me,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">just look at my wound.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

106
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,120
<font color="#ffffff">Did you help her?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

107
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,320
<font color="#ffffff">I'm sorry.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

108
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:02,920
<font color="#ffffff">I just misunderstood.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

109
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,320
<font color="#ffffff">My bad.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

110
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:10,440
<font color="#ffffff">A kiss after a kick?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

111
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:12,080
<font color="#ffffff">Only a fool would let that go.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

112
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:13,880
<font color="#ffffff">Stop it, Sai!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

113
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,640
<font color="#ffffff">Don't do this again.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

114
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:18,400
<font color="#ffffff">I don't want people thinking</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

115
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:20,600
<font color="#ffffff">you're all brawn</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

116
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:22,880
<font color="#ffffff">and no brains.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

117
00:09:24,760 --> 00:09:27,040
<font color="#ffffff">Oops!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

118
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:29,840
<font color="#ffffff">That one has got to hurt.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

119
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:34,400
<font color="#ffffff">All brawn and no… no brains, sir.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

120
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:38,160
<font color="#ffffff">Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

121
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:40,400
<font color="#ffffff">I know</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

122
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,720
<font color="#ffffff">you're poor.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

123
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:47,000
<font color="#ffffff">You won't get hurt for nothing.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

124
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:49,000
<font color="#ffffff">Let's…</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

125
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:51,840
<font color="#ffffff">Just let Mud handle your medical bill.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

126
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,360
<font color="#ffffff">Sorry.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

127
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,320
<font color="#ffffff">Petch.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

128
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:04,040
<font color="#ffffff">Are you okay?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

129
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,160
<font color="#ffffff">Put some ice on it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

130
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:15,640
<font color="#ffffff">Shoot!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

131
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:18,120
<font color="#ffffff">It hurts just looking at it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

132
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:22,080
<font color="#ffffff">It's just a minor bruise. I'm fine.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

133
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,640
<font color="#ffffff">Your body is fine,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

134
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:27,480
<font color="#ffffff">but what about your feelings?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

135
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:30,960
<font color="#ffffff">God, I hate Ake so much.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

136
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:33,400
<font color="#ffffff">He's rich and rotten.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

137
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:37,520
<font color="#ffffff">If I ever get rich,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">I'll make him bow to you 300 times.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

138
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:39,920
<font color="#ffffff">Stop thinking about him, Sai.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

139
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,120
<font color="#ffffff">He's not worth it.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

140
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:43,880
<font color="#ffffff">Wait.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

141
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:49,160
<font color="#ffffff">There's one more thing.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

142
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,680
<font color="#ffffff">What?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

143
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:53,680
<font color="#ffffff">How did you run into that bi--</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

144
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:55,000
<font color="#ffffff">I mean, that girl, Dao?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

145
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,080
<font color="#ffffff">Right.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

146
00:10:57,520 --> 00:10:59,880
<font color="#ffffff">You said you had errands this morning.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

147
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:02,400
<font color="#ffffff">Were you meeting Dao?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

148
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:07,280
<font color="#ffffff">I swear it wasn't planned.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

149
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:11,680
<font color="#ffffff">I was bringing things to my dad</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">and ran into her by chance.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

150
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:12,800
<font color="#ffffff">That's all.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

151
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:15,160
<font color="#ffffff">Dao went to see Mr. Nop?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

152
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:19,400
<font color="#ffffff">What? Why did she go to your house?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

153
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:21,480
<font color="#ffffff">Did you two know each other before?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

154
00:11:21,560 --> 00:11:22,640
<font color="#ffffff">Sai,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

155
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,360
<font color="#ffffff">whether we did or not,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

156
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,960
<font color="#ffffff">it was just a coincidence.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

157
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:28,080
<font color="#ffffff">Nothing more. Got it?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

158
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:30,360
<font color="#ffffff">But I don't trust that rich girl.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

159
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:31,960
<font color="#ffffff">Sai,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

160
00:11:32,560 --> 00:11:34,120
<font color="#ffffff">you're obsessing over this.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

161
00:11:35,160 --> 00:11:36,960
<font color="#ffffff">Drop this nonsense.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

162
00:11:37,680 --> 00:11:38,720
<font color="#ffffff">It's a waste of time.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

163
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,560
<font color="#ffffff">Let's go practice.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

164
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:49,640
<font color="#ffffff">Jealous women aren't his type.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

165
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:51,000
<font color="#ffffff">Shut up!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

166
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:58,240
<font color="#ffffff">What's so great about that girl, anyway?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

167
00:11:58,840 --> 00:12:00,720
<font color="#ffffff">Why does he keep defending her?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

168
00:12:01,400 --> 00:12:02,520
<font color="#ffffff">Darn it!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

169
00:12:15,040 --> 00:12:15,880
<font color="#ffffff">Dao.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

170
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:18,240
<font color="#ffffff">I've cleared everything up.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

171
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:20,360
<font color="#ffffff">I hope you won't bring up the past again.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

172
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:23,920
<font color="#ffffff">I'm not here to talk about the past.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

173
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:27,160
<font color="#ffffff">I'm here to take care of my fiancée.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

174
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:32,440
<font color="#ffffff">How is your wound? Should we see a doctor?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

175
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:33,720
<font color="#ffffff">No need.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

176
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:50,840
<font color="#ffffff">Don't, Ake!</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

