00:24:47,680 --> 00:24:48,560
<font color="#ffffff">This one?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

354
00:24:49,360 --> 00:24:51,560
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, careful.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

355
00:24:54,600 --> 00:24:55,800
<font color="#ffffff">Where did you get these?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

356
00:24:55,880 --> 00:24:58,640
<font color="#ffffff">From the musicians who used to play here.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

357
00:24:58,720 --> 00:25:03,160
<font color="#ffffff">They were broke,</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">so they pawned their guitars to me.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

358
00:25:04,280 --> 00:25:07,760
<font color="#ffffff">So you're saying</font><font color="#ffffff">
