396
00:26:32,560 --> 00:26:37,360
<font color="#ffffff">The suit rental could've been free</font><font color="#ffffff">
<font color="#ffffff">from the start.<font color="#ffffff"></font></font></font>

397
00:26:37,440 --> 00:26:39,440
<font color="#ffffff">Tell you what. I changed my mind.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

398
00:26:39,520 --> 00:26:40,880
