515
00:33:15,840 --> 00:33:16,960
<font color="#ffffff">By the way,</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

516
00:33:17,040 --> 00:33:19,200
<font color="#ffffff">have you found Petch yet?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

